## Kaizo COokie Clicker

Minified (Paste into console)
```var doc=document.innerHTML,alaunch=new Game.Achievement("New Player","Launched Kaizo Cookie Clicker.",[29,2],0),aprice=new Game.Achievement("Price Inflation","Buy an item that has increased in base price by 20 cookies.",[29,2],0),apatience=new Game.Achievement("Patience","Buy the farm.",[29,2],0),adisappointed=new Game.Achievement("Disappointment","Buy a cursor.",[29,2],0),apain=new Game.Achievement("Pain","Buy a grandma.",[29,2],0);Game.registerMod("Kaizo Cookie Clicker",{init:function(){for(o in l("bakerySubtitle")||l("bakeryName").insertAdjacentHTML("afterend",'<div id="bakerySubtitle" class="title" style="text-align:center;position:absolute;left:0px;right:0px;bottom:32px;font-size:12px;pointer-events:none;text-shadow:0px 1px 1px #000,0px 0px 4px #f00;opacity:0.8;"></div>'),l("bakerySubtitle").textContent="Kaizo Cookie Clicker - By RedBigz",Game.registerHook("draw",()=>{Game.bakeryNameL.innerHTML=Game.bakeryName}),Game.registerHook("cps",function(e){return e/10}),Game.registerHook("check",function(){for(o in Game.Objects)a=Game.Objects[o],a.basePrice+=1,a.refresh(),a.bought>0&&("Grandma"==o&&Game.Win("Pain"),"Cursor"==o&&Game.Win("Disappointment"),"Farm"==o&&Game.Win("Patience"),a.basePrice-a.realprice>=20&&Game.Win("Price Inflation"))}),Game.registerHook("ticker",function(){return["Your cookies are criticized as 'overpriced'.","Your cookie recipe is terrible.","1% of your neighborhood buys your cookies.","Good luck getting the farm!","Better speedrun this thing! Prices increase every few seconds!"]}),Game.Objects)a=Game.Objects[o],a.basePrice=5*a.basePrice,a.realprice=a.basePrice,a.refresh();Game.Notify("Kaizo Cookie Clicker Mod","By RedBigz"),Game.BGsByChoice[9].pic="storeTile",Game.UpgradesById[414].choicesPick(9),Game.Win("New Player")}}),document.innerHTML=doc;```
